Class ProductServer.Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • nutshell.ProductServer.Task
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    Enclosing class:
    ProductServer

    public class ProductServer.Task
extends Thread
    A "tray" containing both the product query info and the resulting object if successfully queried. Task does not know about the generator. Notice GENERATE and getParamEnv.

        Product generation task defining a product instance and operations on it. In this version, directives can be set but only through '?'
        Parameters:
        productStr -
        instructions - - definition how a product is retrieved and handled thereafter - @see #Actions
        parentLog - - log of the parent task (or main process, a product server)
